1) cd var/www/
2) Activate python virtual environment: source ./remontnik/bin/activate
3) cd ./app/remontnik
4) Checkout latest changes: git pull
5) Install Pillow dependencies:
	sudo apt-get install libtiff5-dev libjpeg8-dev zlib1g-dev libfreetype6-dev liblcms2-dev libwebp-dev tcl8.6-dev tk8.6-dev python-tk
6) Update dependencies: pip install -r requirements.pip
7) Run migrations: python manage.py migrate
8) Run server: nohup python manage.py runserver 0:8000 &
